# Anti-Patterns — Never Do These

**Firma:** HorosCode · **Produkt:** HorosCloud

## Layout & Scope

| Never | Do instead |
|-------|------------|
| Build entire page/screen in one pass | One region per task (`01-workflow`) |
| Merge distinct mockup components into one control | Keep mockup component boundaries |
| Skip Preview for "simple" regions | Always `*Preview.axaml` (`06-ui-preview`) |
| Test only in full MainWindow during Pass 1 | Isolated Preview per region |

## Design Fidelity

| Never | Do instead |
|-------|------------|
| Invent new colors not in mockup | Extract → `design-memory.md` → token |
| Invent new spacing/radius/typography | Match mockup or document new token |
| Use `#RRGGBB` inline in Views | `{DynamicResource Brush...}` |
| "Improve" layout vs mockup | Pixel-perfect copy (`02-pixel-perfect`) |
| Ignore mockup elements as "unnecessary" | Implement every visible element |

## Stack Confusion

| Never | Do instead |
|-------|------------|
| Think in Tailwind (`p-4`, `flex`, `gap-2`) | Avalonia `Padding`, `StackPanel.Spacing`, `Grid` |
| Copy React component structure | Avalonia UserControl + MVVM |
| Use CSS box model mental model | Avalonia layout panels + margins |

## Bad Pattern Example

```xml
<!-- WRONG: Tailwind thinking, inline values, merged components -->
<Border Padding="18" Background="#1a1a2e" CornerRadius="12">
  <StackPanel>
    <!-- Header + Nav + Search merged into one blob -->
    <Grid>...</Grid>
  </StackPanel>
</Border>
```

## Good Pattern Example

```xml
<!-- RIGHT: Tokens, separate components, mockup structure -->
<components:HorosHeaderBar Grid.Row="0"
                           DataContext="{Binding Header}" />
<components:HorosSidebar Grid.Row="1" Grid.Column="0"
                         DataContext="{Binding Sidebar}" />
<components:HorosContentPanel Grid.Row="1" Grid.Column="1"
                            DataContext="{Binding Content}" />
```

## Reporting Anti-Patterns

| Never | Do instead |
|-------|------------|
| Report success without screenshot | Score ≥ 98 with PNG evidence |
| Proceed without Human Approval | Stop at `12-human-approval` |
| Scope creep during review fixes | Fix only listed diffs |

